ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectBrokering Permits Regulations
PrecisBROKERING PERMITS REGULATIONS in order establish that an individual or organization must apply for an individual brokering permit for each of the goods to be brokered by using a form provided by the Minister of Foreign Affairs.
